import React from 'react';
import Helmet from 'react-helmet';
import meta from '../meta';
import favicon from '../images/favicons/favicon.ico';
import ogImage from '../images/icons/logo.png';

const Head = (props) => (
  <Helmet>
    <html lang="en" prefix="og: http://ogp.me/ns#" />
    <title itemProp="name" lang="en">
      {props.title}
    </title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href={favicon} />
    <meta name="description" content={props.description} />
    <meta name="keywords" content={meta.siteKeywords} />
    <meta name="google-site-verification" content={meta.googleVerification} />
    <meta property="og:title" content={props.title} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={props.description} />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content={props.siteUrl} />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content={props.title} />
    <meta property="og:image" content={`${meta.siteUrl}${ogImage}`} />
    <meta property="og:image:width" content="1200" />
    <meta property="og:image:height" content="630" />
    <meta property="og:image:type" content="image/png" />
    <meta property="og:locale" content={meta.siteLanguage} />
    <meta itemProp="name" content={props.title} />
    <meta itemProp="description" content={props.description} />
    <meta itemProp="image" content={`${meta.siteUrl}${ogImage}`} />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:url" content={props.siteUrl} />
    <meta name="twitter:site" content={meta.twitterHandle} />
    <meta name="twitter:creator" content={meta.twitterHandle} />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content={props.title} />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content={props.description} />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content={`${meta.siteUrl}${ogImage}`} />
    <meta name="twitter:image:alt" content={props.title} />
  </Helmet>
);

export default Head;
